&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This document records the decisions taken so far during the pre-study phase. Each decision sets a boundary on what the initial implementation will and will not cover. Any later change to these decisions will affect the &lt;a href="https://avant-tecno-oy-uds-library.pages.avant-tecno-oy.ghe.com/docs/v0.0.1/en/planning/delivery_timeline/"&gt;delivery timeline&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href="https://avant-tecno-oy-uds-library.pages.avant-tecno-oy.ghe.com/docs/v0.0.1/en/planning/repository_structure/"&gt;repository structure&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Repository Structure</title><link>https://avant-tecno-oy-uds-library.pages.avant-tecno-oy.ghe.com/docs/v0.0.1/en/planning/repository_structure/</link><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://avant-tecno-oy-uds-library.pages.avant-tecno-oy.ghe.com/docs/v0.0.1/en/planning/repository_structure/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="overview" class="heading"&gt;Overview&lt;a href="#overview" class="heading__anchor" aria-label="Link to this section" tabindex="-1"&gt;
 &lt;svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;
 &lt;path d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 0 0 1.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 1 1 2.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 .75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 0 0 4.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 .75.75 0 0 0 1.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 0 0-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 4.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0z"/&gt;
 &lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The library is organised as a single Cargo workspace containing several crates. Each crate has one clear responsibility. Backends are not split by operating system, they are split by what they provide to the layer above. A backend either delivers full UDS PDUs to the service layer, or it delivers raw CAN frames to a userspace ISO-TP implementation that then provides the PDUs.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Delivery Timeline</title><link>https://avant-tecno-oy-uds-library.pages.avant-tecno-oy.ghe.com/docs/v0.0.1/en/planning/delivery_timeline/</link><pubDate>Mon, 18 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://avant-tecno-oy-uds-library.pages.avant-tecno-oy.ghe.com/docs/v0.0.1/en/planning/delivery_timeline/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="phases" class="heading"&gt;Phases&lt;a href="#phases" class="heading__anchor" aria-label="Link to this section" tabindex="-1"&gt;
