 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="phase-1---pre-study" class="heading"&gt;Phase 1 - Pre-study&lt;a href="#phase-1---pre-study" class="heading__anchor" aria-label="Link to this section" tabindex="-1"&gt;
