&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Target: w20-w24 (13 May - 13 June 2026) (some team members are in vacations so not the whole period is used)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Existing UDS Libraries</title><link>https://avant-tecno-oy-uds-library.pages.avant-tecno-oy.ghe.com/docs/v0.0.1/en/planning/existing_libraries/</link><pubDate>Mon, 18 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://avant-tecno-oy-uds-library.pages.avant-tecno-oy.ghe.com/docs/v0.0.1/en/planning/existing_libraries/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="automotive_diag" class="heading"&gt;automotive_diag&lt;a href="#automotive_diag" class="heading__anchor" aria-label="Link to this section" tabindex="-1"&gt;
 &lt;svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;
 &lt;path d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 0 0 1.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 1 1 2.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 .75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 0 0 4.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 .75.75 0 0 0 1.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 0 0-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 4.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0z"/&gt;
